== About me
\n
My name is Angelo Rodio. I am a third-year PhD student working on [https://www.theses.fr/s318701 "Resource-Aware Federated Learning"] under the guidance of [http://www-sop.inria.fr/members/Giovanni.Neglia/ Dr. Giovanni Neglia] and [http://www-sop.inria.fr/members/Alain.Jean-Marie/ Prof. Alain Jean-Marie] at Inria Sophia-Antipolis (Team [https://team.inria.fr/neo/team-members/ NEO]).

My PhD scholarship is generously funded by [https://3ia.univ-cotedazur.eu 3IA Côte d'Azur], one of France's leading "Interdisciplinary Institutes for Artificial Intelligence."

I specialize in *distributed* and *federated learning* systems. My research focuses on designing large-scale federated learning algorithms for efficient data and system utilization, with particular emphasis on wireless networks and resource constraints. \n
I employ mathematical tools from distributed optimization and statistical learning theory.

